_:N276a05080f1744c5a745e7e2efdee3cf <http://schema.org/description> "We’re responsible for regulating environmental and decommissioning activity for offshore oil and gas operations, including carbon capture and storage operations, on the UK continental shelf. OPRED is part of the Department for Energy Security and Net Zero ." .
